From f842f449bf48e6e90de789f27bdd7ca6e93f217f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vincent Cruz <mooz@blockos.org>
Date: Fri, 20 Mar 2026 16:33:08 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 07/10] Install mepa common source code.

Install mepa/common to <install_dir>/include/mepa.
Add a function in CMake package script to create custom mepa libraries.
Driver targets now embedded MEPA_HAS_<drv> compile definition.

Signed-off-by: Vincent Cruz <mooz@blockos.org>
---
 .cmake/mepaConfig.cmake.in            | 31 +++++++++++++++++-
 mepa/.cmake/mepa-macros.cmake         |  2 +-
 mepa/CMakeLists.txt                   | 47 ++++++++-------------------
 mepa/aqr/CMakeLists.txt               |  1 +
 mepa/dummy_phy/CMakeLists.txt         |  1 +
